parameters: ピッキングで解錠する

If you have a \C[2]lock-picking tool\C[0] and a
\C[2]hairpin\C[0], you might be able to challenge
unlocking the door...
You're Noah, right? Pull yourself together...!

Are you feeling disoriented?! It's dangerous...
but why...? This child's body won't move.

Are you Remi?! I wonder if you're the master of
this pond.

This sacrifice is of my own will... It has come
here... Do not interfere...

What's going on...?! I came here to help at the
request of Noah's friend, Edda!

......It's none of your business... hurry... go
back... because it's what I wanted...

What...?! But being a sacrifice means... dying
here, right?

I will offer myself to Remi-sama... and... all of
me will be saved... This is salvation.
That's right... Outsiders should leave promptly.

I'm sorry, but I can't just go back like this. I
can't ignore Edda's request.
Those who oppose me... shall not be forgiven...
I managed to defeat them, but...

Noah, are you really conscious and did you really
come here on your own?
Remi-sama... is dead... how could this...

Edda is waiting upstairs. For now, let's just go
back.

Hehehe... Go back...? What are you talking
about... I will become the next Remi.

In the end, I couldn't save her... I have no
choice but to report to Edda, who is waiting at
the entrance.
Not as much as you talk...

Ahh... With this... I will become one with Remi-
sama... and all of our wishes... will come true...

I don't understand the reason... but if it's their
own will... I have no choice but to respect it...

Thank you... I absolutely must accomplish it... My
final wish... It will come true with this...

If you could just tell Edda that I'll be fine...
Thank you, unknown magical girl...

There might be some circumstances... I need to
report to Edda, who is waiting at the entrance for
now...
